What you need to know:

Despite an upturn in form of late inspired by the emergence of youngsters Emile Smith Rowe and Bukayo Saka, Arsenal sit eighth in the Premier League and out of both domestic cup competitions.Even as his appearances on the field diminished under Arteta and his predecessor Unai Emery, the shadow of Ozil has continued to hang over the club.Isco, James Rodriguez, Gareth Bale and Odegaard's new teammate Dani Ceballos have also struggled for minutes under the Frenchman.